# API
API connection is a requested feature for connecting
your wallet address to your crypto node for "TT"
Thunder Token is a token that is connected to your 
ETH address 0x is the beginning of your eth address.
Eth blockchain can be found on https://blockchain.com
This web address is on Google or any internet browser

Your API connection safely links your IP address an
wallet address together for a secure connection 
allowing your user to look at the blockchain and 
transactions that are being processed.

File hash logs will be stored on blockchain for later 
review an tax related purposes for users to check 
there accounts 
